{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762173180504","path":null,"data":{"id":676,"title":"Manulife：創富傳承保障2推出15年及整付年期以及延長整付保費產品推廣期","type":"PRODUCT_PROMOTION","time":1636357319916,"tags":["宏利金融"],"content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">致合作夥伴：</p> \n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 一、「創富傳承保障計劃2」推出<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">整付</span>及<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">15年</span>保費繳付期</strong></p> \n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 於2021年11月8日推出<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">整付</span></strong>及<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">15年</span></strong>保費繳付期，整付保費<strong>提供首日退保價值達整付保費之80%</strong>以作保費融資。同時，</p> \n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\"> \n <li><strong><span style=\"color: #5b2ecd;\">升級</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">豐譽傳承保障計劃 2 / 創富傳承保障計劃 2&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #009fff;\">(保費繳付期五年或以上)</span></span></strong>的客戶推廣：首3年合共可享高達<strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">&nbsp;24%</span></strong>保費折扣</li> \n <li><strong style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #5b2ecd;\">新增</span><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">創富傳承保障計劃 2 (整付保費)</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;的客戶推廣：高達<strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">&nbsp;4%</span></strong>保費折扣優惠。</span></li> \n</ul> \n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 二、延長</span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">豐譽傳承保障計劃 2<span style=\"color: #009fff;\">（整付保費）</span>推廣期</span></span></strong></p> \n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;推廣期將由2021年11月5日<strong>延長至2022年1月3日</strong></span></span></span></p> \n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 三、涉及不同自願醫保計劃的更改保障計劃之健康折扣轉移</strong></p> \n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>由2021年11月8日起，</strong>就<strong><span style=\"color: #5b2ecd;\">涉及不同自願醫保計劃的更改保障計劃</span></strong>而言，用作計算原有保障中<strong><span style=\"color: #5b2ecd;\">健康折扣</span></strong>的相關時期將會<span style=\"color: #5b2ecd;\"><strong>轉移</strong></span>至新保障；其後保單年度新保障之健康折扣，亦會按照該相關時期計算。</span></p> \n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/7970577996447744/6601c3676348462e88c4ac95b725cebb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></span></p> \n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"NewsFlash.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2021-11-08/12859e22685040fd97b227b32fe63a3d.pdf","uploadTime":1636357381650,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"附件1.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2021-11-08/8e8ef2a19e2c4a379ff4610a180bb59d.pdf","uploadTime":1636357381704,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName